casebody.data:
Donna S. SEEK, Plaintiff,
v.
Theodore R. SHALACK, Defendant-Movant. M-459/460/461/462 September Term 2018
079628 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-459) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motions for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-460), to expand the record (M-461), and to file a supplemental brief (M-462) are denied.
